    "type": "message",
    "text": "I agree that standards support and fighting monopoly are important, and deserve effort from a \"hacker\" point of view. And this work would have been perfect if it follows standards. But, I really enjoy this hacking attitude where one try to understand technology by ripping it appart and use it to do anything you want for your own pleasure. And without anything/anyone tell you what is the best way to do it or teach you.",
